cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DL, cs.SE 

This paper discusses a Datalog-based system for performing complex logic reasoning tasks, specifically for knowledge graphs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also mentions the use of ontological reasoning, which falls under the category of Description Logics (cs.DL). Finally, the paper discusses the implementation and performance of the system, which could also fall under the category of Software Engineering (cs.SE).
